nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A lively monkey energetically bounces on a neatly made bed, its limbs splayed in mid-air. As the monkey lands, the bed creases slightly under its weight, and it quickly prepares for another joyful leap, its eyes wide with excitement and mischief.
This scheduler is made for models using lightx loras. You can find it here: https://github.com/BigStationW/flowmatch_scheduler-comfyui
The lora at 5.6 generates more motion but speeds up the fps too
Encode WanVideo, TTM Latent Add, CFGFloatListScheduler come from Kijai's wanvideo-wrapper
You can find the lora here: https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/tree/main/Lightx2v
If you have enough vram you can use bigger versions (fp8, etc) or quantizations (q8, etc) of the model
